name: Gym Challenge Theme Deck - "Blaine"
extCardText:
Set up to the Gym Challenge expansion! Join forces with Giovanni, Sabrina, Koga, and Blaine to go for the challenge! Each Gym Challenge preconstructed theme deck teams you with a different gym leader to create an all-new Pokémon trading card game adventure.

In the Blaine theme deck, feel the burn with Blaine and his Fire Pokémon!

This deck contains a combination of cards from the Base Set 2, Gym Heroes, and Gym Challenge expansions: 28 Gym Challenge Energy cards; 3 Gym Heroes cards, with some duplicates; 5 Base Set 2 cards, with some duplicates; and 24 Gym Challange cards other than Energy, with some duplicates; for a total of 60 cards.
